# Client SDK build outputs (generated, never committed). The generated wasm
# packages, TS build, Python native artifacts, and stub caches are all rebuilt
# from `crates/sdk-core`. COMMITTED source-of-truth that must NOT be ignored:
#   conformance/vectors.json, conformance/*.hex,
#   bindings/py/python/dexos/_core.pyi, bindings/ts/src/wire.ts
bindings/wasm/pkg/
bindings/ts/wasm/
bindings/ts/dist/
dist/
**/*.so
**/*.pyd
**/__pycache__/
**/.pytest_cache/
